One mosque collapsed, two schools and one home damaged in East Luwu Regency.

At least 20 homes destroyed and many others damaged in Yüksekova District, Turkey.

One structure collapsed and 39 others damaged in Kara-Suu-Alay area.

One home destroyed in Lebak Regency.

Indonesia, North Sumatra, 41 km (25 mi) ENE of Sibolga

At least 20 homes destroyed, 47 others and a church damaged and roads affected in the Achoma-Lari-Maca area.

Several homes and a caravanserai collapsed and many buildings damaged in the Natanz area.

At least 13 structures damaged in Chiriquí, Herrera, and Veraguas provinces.
